\f2\b0\fs21 \cf2 Illustration of me be baptized in water with alligators\
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}People in Florida tend to be way more comfortable with alligators than the rest of the country?  Why?  Because they are around them so often and so much\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Let me show you some picture of people way too comfortable with alligators\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Gator pic 1\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Gator pic 3\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Gator pic 2\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What we know is this though\'85it\'92s only a matter of time before he gets bit\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
