\fs32 \cf0 WE\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f2\b0\fs21 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}See, I have alligators in my life\'85you have alligators\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Things that we have become so comfortable with that we don\'92t take seriously as a problem anymore\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And others around us\'85they see it.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s clear to them and they may have even said something to us\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But we justify and blow it off\'85because it\'92s just Fred\'85Fred\'92s never hurt anyone yet and it\'92s ok.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But the tension is we can handle it and it isn\'92t hurting anyone and it\'92s cute and you like it Fred\'85Fred would never hurt anyone over here.  They just don\'92t know Fred like you do.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So here\'92s the question \'96 what is it in your life that you\'92ve become comfortable with?\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}That if you were honest \'96 it\'92s not a big deal but\'85\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I may drink a little\'85not a lot\'85too much sometimes\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I may eat a little\'85not a lot\'85too much sometimes\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I may allow certain thoughts to linger in my mind too long\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I might use\'85not abuse\'85but use prescription drugs too much\'85but it\'92s not a problem\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I might be a little arrogant\'85but come on who doesn\'92t take a little pride in what they do\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I might get a little angry and yell every now and then but it isn\'92t a problem\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I might talk a little too much about other people when they aren\'92t around but who doesn\'92t do that.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And your and my justification is simple\'85no one\'92s got hurt yet!\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The reason we mess around with them is because we don\'92t think they\'92re dangerous\'85a thought pattern isn\'92t that bad\'85what\'92s the big deal.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
