\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 17\'a0
\f4\b0\fs24 \nosupersub \'93Don\'92t you see that whatever enters the mouth goes into the stomach and then out of the body?\'a0\
\

\f3\b\fs18 \super 18\'a0
\f4\b0\fs24 \nosupersub But the things that come out of a person\'92s mouth come from the heart,\'a0and these defile them.\'a0\
\
\

\f3\b\fs18 \super 19\'a0
\f4\b0\fs24 \nosupersub For out of the heart come evil thoughts\'97murder, adultery, sexual immorality, theft, false testimony, slander.\'a0
\f3\b\fs18 \super 20\'a0
\f4\b0\fs24 \nosupersub These are what defile a person;\'94  Matthew 15\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f2\fs21 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Now\'85that is where it comes from but what do you do about that?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s one thing to know where it is, it\'92s a whole other issue to deal with it.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And so Solomon\'85smartest man to ever live, wrote a few books and collection of thoughts and put them together and in one of them he wrote something incredibly important.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f4\fs24 \cf4 Above all else, \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
