\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}List of questions I heard a while ago:\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Is everything ok in your heart?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You mad at anyone?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Are you waiting around for someone to come to you to make things right?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Have you had any extended imaginary conversations with someone lately?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Do things come out of your mouth that you have to apologize for?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Have you secretly celebrated someone else\'92s failure in the past few weeks?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Got any secrets?\
