\f2\b0\fs21 \cf2 Illustration of Joey our drummer now\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sb240\sa240\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f4\fs18 \cf6 As some of you may or may not know I have decided to quit the current band I am in and moved on! I have been in the bar scene for about 10 years now and I have noticed its a long road to no where! 90% of the places are dumps and 99% of the musicians are egotistical pompous *******! I have been playing music for over 15 years and I know for a fact God did not give me this talent to play for 3 toothless drunks in a rat hole bar! My talent was given to me to play for him that is exactly what I am going to do! I have never felt so free to not be attached to a band and the bar scene! From this day forward I will not touch a drumstick unless I know for a fact that it's to glorify my God! Peace and Love my friends!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f2\fs21 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Now it would have been easy for him to justify what he was doing and there\'92s no verse against playing in a bar\'85and drunk people need music too and\'85.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But what I think is awesome is not what he did\'85that\'92s cool\'85he had an alligator and he killed it\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f4 \cf7 This popped up in my memories today and made me smile! Last year on this day I made my mind up to quit my band and quit playing in bars! I said I was only going to use my talents for God since he was the one that gave them to me and that's exactly what I have done! But get this in 1 year God has turned my life upside down in the best way possible! Kathy and I struggled with infertility for 7 and half years and now I have a beautiful daughter and another one on the way! She will be here in January! On top of that he has blessed us with the exact house that we have wanted for years and years! He worked it out where we could sell our house and buy the only other house in our town that we wanted! I believe this all happened because I was obedient to what God wanted for me! I thank him for all he has and will do for me and my family!\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

